@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v2
    v1 = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.64 - v0 + 0.48)) * 0.11)
    tmp = (((v1 + 0.93 + tmp + 0.89) * wp.exp(v1 + 0.07)) + wp.sin((tmp + 0.73 * v2 + 0.88)))
    v2 = 0.88
    v2 = (v2 * wp.abs(wp.exp(tmp + 0.36)))
    v1 = 0.92
    data[tid] = v0
